revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yearys}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yeary'' is the 11223<sup>rd</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 2818 individuals. ''Yeary'' is most common among White (91.48%) individuals.
